  <brief_title>Obstructive Sleep Apnea and Venous Thromboembolism</brief_title>
  <acronym>OSAVTE</acronym>
  <official_title>Patients With Obstructive Sleep Apnea (OSA), Independent of Obesity, Are at Increased Risk of Venous Thromboembolic Events (VTE)</official_title>
